title: Refrigerator Ice Chute Door
description: Refrigerator Ice Chute Door ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 4 Reviews PartSelect Number PS1526426 Manufacturer Part Number 241688401 An ice chute is mounted to the interior panel and extends between the interior panel opening and the dispenser opening for transferring ice through the chute door.
symptoms: Ice maker dispenses too much ice

installationInstructions.author: Shelby from Clinton, IL
installationInstructions.title: The ice chute door didn't close all the timed
installationInstructions.content: The door has nylon gear teeth that wore out and needed replaced.  The ice chute came off very easy with 6 screws.  I used a punch and pliers to remove the hinge pin.  Then the door came off and the new one put on.  Very easy.  The part was ordered on Sunday and arrived on Tuesday.
